pycat steals Dawn’s place in the home—forcing Dawn onto the streets.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622350/extras/cd76d6fed892db697b1dfe2e6b49b5f4.poster.avif?t=1763430983\" width=560 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622350/extras/cd76d6fed892db697b1dfe2e6b49b5f4.webm?t=1763430983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622350/extras/cd76d6fed892db697b1dfe2e6b49b5f4.mp4?t=1763430983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wander alleyways, fences and rooftops as you learn about the true meaning of home. The reflective pacing of the game allows you the opportunity to indulge in the emotions of love, loneliness and letting go as you progress throughout the story.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622350/extras/151df1b6a6739462ffb8d29f7ceb4ca3.poster.avif?t=1763430983\" width=560 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622350/extras/151df1b6a6739462ffb8d29f7ceb4ca3.webm?t=1763430983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622350/extras/151df1b6a6739462ffb8d29f7ceb4ca3.mp4?t=1763430983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Copycat is fully voice acted, featuring hours of dialogue and a talented voice cast. Original music score by Daniel Bunting.</p>",
